data.description: Nestled on 2.4 acres of privacy & tranquility your custom rambler awaits! Inside greets you with an open concept layout, vaulted ceilings, gleaming hardwood floors & fine details throughout. Stunning chefs kitchen with new appliances, custom fixtures & walk-in pantry. Luxurious primary suite with updated ensuite bath & walk-in closet. 4th bedroom has built-in media system & custom bunk beds, offering endless possibilities! Backyard oasis with new deck, BBQ area & fire pit for relaxed gatherings. Surrounded by nature's serenity, this property embodies the PNW lifestyle at its finest! Near schools, parks & easy HWY access!
